//www.ctwant.com/article/89668</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37399aa53f5c6bd59dc0a0b9e2d4eff8043252b1","tid":2318191,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:04:42.000Z","msg":"拜登：冇就職典禮到1月20號都會宣誓做總統 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511d2b824d7d9943d565e400e057e8b488db93fb","tid":2318191,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:04:47.000Z","msg":"搞到咁<br />\n點解啲港媒仲可以當登做硬"},{"pid":"7cc68cf52d828acf64edf12a982555f3e496c944","tid":2318191,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:05:59.000Z","msg":"但侵侵輸左, 法院都唔受理"},{"pid":"cc2342bca4095b0b98251b3e42351754f0695916","tid":2318191,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"511d2b824d7d9943d565e400e057e8b488db93fb","tid":2318191,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:04:47.000Z","msg":"搞到咁<br />\n點解啲港媒仲可以當登做硬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:06:44.000Z","msg":"製造既定事實希望強姦大眾思想，同過去四年塑造當奴侵係種族歧視者一樣。"},{"pid":"00404f2febc45be526b2f1553a4cd08b230bcb6b","tid":2318191,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c15a1fb567a3971c814a080771474b94c1a0564","tid":2318191,"uid":382841,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:08:40.000Z","msg":"緊係拒絕確認<br />\n侵先係真正既總統"},{"pid":"4e2db8fb4d5acccb9b457c62af1a0edbbe1f32d0","tid":2318191,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:19:46.000Z","msg":"其實都係睇選舉人投票"},{"pid":"fa91f3114cacdb9f4ad613cf11b2ac1dff0fa667","tid":2318191,"uid":25673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cc68cf52d8